name: ARMANI
description: Armani Le Parfum: an unexpected floral fragrance, a sensuous aura. An exquisite, well balanced composition of 80 different rare and precious essences. The fresh and spicy top note of this fragrance culminates in a rich bouquet of floral essences enhanced by green and fruity notes which finally blossom out, exuding the precious, vibrant scents of the woody essences.
